            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Marti <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Turus Longini <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>sacerdotali</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>pro suis et <expan><abbr>cognation</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Nantania <lb n="6"/>de suo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundort: Südostliburnien; am ehesten Varvaria (Bribir) oder Burnum (Ivoševci). (B): AE 1964: Z. 1: sacr(um). Z. 3: dec(urio) et sacerdotali(s) bezieht sich auf das Vorsteher- und Priesteramt des Turus in der cognatio Nantania.</p>
            </div>
